# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_bb4de9c3 (line 83428)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_bb4de9c3:
    # "Frequently taken by the goblin, and frequently offering herself to him, it was only a matter of time."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_ea006719 (line 83435)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_ea006719:
    # "The coupling of goblin and human was said to only rarely produce offspring."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_f75aa75b (line 83436)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_f75aa75b:
    # "But such low chances had been offset by the frequent nature of their mating."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_53ac90f4 (line 83437)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_53ac90f4:
    # "Her belly began to swell, with passing weaks, more and more."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_d140edac (line 83438)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_d140edac:
    # "Her belly expanded, her ankles swole up, and she suffered the morning sickness."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_d3174ca8 (line 83439)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_d3174ca8:
    # "Still, the cage remained her home, though the sweet taste of the drink made it impossible to worry of such things."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_3a532a03 (line 83440)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_3a532a03:
    # "Instead, Sarah laid blissfully on the floor of the cage, lost to blind happiness as she felt her child inside of her."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_50a9711e (line 83441)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_50a9711e:
    # "The goblin, father to her brood, did not abade in his desire."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_411a86d4 (line 83442)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_411a86d4:
    # "And as Sarah grew larger and fatter, rapidly, she became ever more immobile."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_40001566 (line 83443)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_40001566:
    # "She laid, staring up at the night sky, as all the world spun about her, pulsing and dancing to the drink's influence."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_90f28067 (line 83444)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_90f28067:
    # "Soon, she would bear him children."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_394ff552 (line 83445)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_394ff552:
    # "And, she hoped, Gods willing she would give him so many more."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_6d5c0d66 (line 83446)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_6d5c0d66:
    # "So ends the story of Sarah Rose."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_192914a8 (line 83447)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_192914a8:
    # "Princess to mage. Traitor to her teacher. Goblin wife."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_7c76711e (line 83448)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_7c76711e:
    # "The End."
    ""

